title: Santa Cruz Jammers
description: While in Hawaii, the Santa Cruz team (Emmanuel Guzman, Shuriken Shannon, Justin Strubing, Sid Melvin, Eric Dressen and Salba) cruz on the new Jammin' Jammer through the legendary Wallows ditch on their way to the beach.
